{"title":"矿工二唱","authors":["邓华"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":9,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工二唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸽哨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最使人动情的——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是和黎明一同诞生的鸽哨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那翱翔在蓝空的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的精灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刹那，映亮了与早晨一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象忠诚的跋涉者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟情道路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工最爱太阳和天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使在幽晦如夜的煤井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那轰轰隆隆的风钻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也驱不退萦绕耳际的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸽哨声声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，哨声划过头顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正奋翅飞向红宝石般的天穹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的心，一点一点地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接近太阳——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那感情中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜红鲜红的神圣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难得寻的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样一片葱茏的草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂喜的瞳孔青翠欲滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五分钟的淋浴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲掉了一天的沉重和疲惫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来到山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让格崩格崩响的筋骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横袒在夕阳洒下的金辉里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黝黑的饥渴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大口大口地呼吸着绿风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和青青的馥郁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了输出而摄入"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了奉献而汲取"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，粗张的血管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新贮满汹涌豪放的活力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个红色的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都被染成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧绿碧绿"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}